TITLE: Preventing RTL Flipping with @noflip
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to prevent automatic flipping of properties in RTL mode by using the /* @noflip */ CSS comment. This ensures the property will be applied the same in both LTR and RTL layouts.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/griffel/blob/main/packages/react/README.md#2025-04-23_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
import { makeStyles } from '@griffel/react';

const useClasses = makeStyles({
  root: {
    paddingLeft: '10px /* @noflip */',
  },
});
```

