TITLE: Creating Monolithic CSS with makeResetStyles in Griffel
DESCRIPTION: Basic example of using makeResetStyles to create monolithic CSS styles including hover states. This returns a React hook that generates a single CSS class containing all style declarations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/griffel/blob/main/apps/website/docs/react/api/make-reset-styles.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

