TITLE: Automatic RTL Support with makeStyles
DESCRIPTION: Shows how Griffel automatically flips CSS properties and values for Right-To-Left text direction. Properties like padding-left will become padding-right in RTL mode.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/griffel/blob/main/packages/react/README.md#2025-04-23_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
